<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Burt's Links | heyitsburt.com</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1a1a1a, #2a2a2a, #1a1a1a);
            background-size: 200% 200%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 2px solid #ffffff;
        }

        .name {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .about {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #cccccc;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .link-button {
            display: block;
            background-color: #333333;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .link-button:hover {
            background-color: #444444;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://github.com/josephburt.png" alt="Joseph Burt's Profile" class="profile-img">
        <div class="name">Hey, It's Burt!</div>
        <div class="about">
            Hey there! I'm Joseph Burt, and this is my corner of the internet where I showcase my projects, share my thoughts, and everything else that inspires me. Glad you dropped by!
        </div>
        
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@JosephBurt-Main" class="link-button">YouTube</a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/heyitsburt" class="link-button">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://facebook.com/heyitsburtcom" class="link-button">Facebook</a>
        <a href="https://twitch.tv/heyitsjburt" class="link-button">Twitch</a>
        <a href="https://tiktok.com/@hey_its_burt" class="link-button">TikTok</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/josephburt" class="link-button">X</a>
        <a href="https://cash.app/$misterburt" class="link-button">CashApp</a>
        <a href="https://venmo.com/u/JosephBurt" class="link-button">Venmo</a>
